Primary analyses · Overweight/Obesity
==============================================================================
  Analytic cohort: n = 2,461, incident cases = 457 (18.6%)

--- Between-person analyses ---
  (no multiple-comparison correction across the three rhythm parameters)
  Typical-day mesor         OR = 1.30, 95% CI [1.17, 1.45], p = 1.04e-06
  Typical-day amplitude     OR = 0.91, 95% CI [0.82, 1.01], p = 0.0782
  Typical-day acrophase     OR = 1.12, 95% CI [1.01, 1.24], p = 0.0337

--- Within-person analyses ---
  SD daily mesor            n = 2228  cases = 407  univariate OR = 1.21, 95% CI [1.09, 1.34], p = 0.000374
  SD daily mesor            joint with mesor: feature OR = 1.23 [1.11, 1.35], p = 7.47e-05; mesor OR = 1.33, p = 6.63e-07
  SD daily amplitude        n = 2228  cases = 407  univariate OR = 1.12, 95% CI [1.00, 1.24], p = 0.0485
  SD daily amplitude        joint with mesor: feature OR = 1.20 [1.06, 1.35], p = 0.00457; mesor OR = 1.37, p = 1.3e-07
  SD daily acrophase        n = 2228  cases = 407  univariate OR = 1.22, 95% CI [1.10, 1.34], p = 8.9e-05
